IceCity v0.1.9f (beta) [21.12.2004]
by Andre Schmidt (pikkukakkonen@arcor.de)

FileName    : fy_icecity019f.bsp
MapType     : Counter Strike Source "Fight Yard"
SpawnPoints : 16/CT 16/T
KnownBugs   : "high shadow" see through walls

My first map for CS:S, you may notice that the map "base design" is from 
"fy_icecity", who didn't play that :)

The "flying canisters" on the roof was created using this awesome video
tutorial: http://www.hl2modcentral.com/tutorial.php?id=32&cat=0

because the map has a "high shadow" bug, i wont be editing this map until i
get a GFX card that supports "high shadows", so that i can correct 
the bug (and see the results).

cheers,
andre
